            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1684845460020-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>beef mince</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>chopped shallot</strong>, <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong>,<strong> half</strong> the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>ginger </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a small pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Divide the <strong>beef mince</strong> into 3 per person<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and shape them into <strong>meatballs</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1684845464386-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
