    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>red Thai-style beef meatball bake</strong> and garnish with the <strong>chilli</strong> <strong>rounds </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Tip: Watch out for any cardamom pods!</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
